<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.figma.com">Website creating with Figma</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://jekyllrb.com">Mantain blogs and static websites with jekyll</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/hotwired/turbo">Mobile website creation with Turbo</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.getpostman.com">Postman client to automate rest api testing</a></li>
</ul>

