<h4 id="ios">iOS</h4>

<ul>
  <li>Try to avoid using third party frameworks.</li>
  <li>When third party framework is need user <a href="https://swift.org/package-manager/">Swift Package Manager</a> or <a href="https://github.com/Carthage/Carthage">Carthage</a>, avoid CocoaPods .</li>
  <li><a href="https://developer.apple.com">iOS development native</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/realm/SwiftLint">Swiftlint code quality</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/turbolinks/turbolinks-ios">Website creation for an ios app with turbolinks</a></li>
</ul>

